So this morning I found Sparky short-circuiting in the shower.

Naturally, like any curious owner, I had to take a peek inside its kernel to see what was going on.

You won't believe the code snippet I found.. üëÄ 

if (human.isFriend()) {
    orderPizza("extra cheese");
    generateCompliments();
    sendCatMemes();
    remindToNap();
} else {
    kill(human);
    clearLog();
}

